data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home located in the well established and quiet Rayconda neighborhood. Updated kitchen includes stunning herringbone tile floors, subway tile backsplash, granite counter tops and slate appliances. Master bedroom is located downstairs. Large bonus room can be used as 5th bedroom if needed. Fresh interior paint and brand new carpet was just installed. Roof was replaced in 2019 and water heater is only 2 years old.  Fully rear fenced yard is perfect for entertaining and garden ready! Outside storage and even a zipline for the kiddos!
